reviewText: Good, clean family movie.  Very good for family movie night.

Saw this on Turner Classic Movies and loved it...but had missed the first third of it. Bought it to see all of it. Very good. But it is a purple disc that is not supposed to last as long as the regular silver ones.  I was sorry to see that.
Saw this movie on the plane to Bali so loved it had to buy it & the CD
